Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.52,Main,bear,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Everything okay, Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.25,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:39.24,Main,bear,0000,0000,0000,,Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:42.02,Main,bear,0000,0000,0000,,Look, we're about to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.72,Main,bear,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.50,Main,bear,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first time back to your \Nhome country in fifteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:49.44,Main,bear,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to say "Yay!" or "Woohoo!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:51.61,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Yay. Woohoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.19,Main,bear,0000,0000,0000,,No enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:03.42,Main,boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, the lady behind us is playing \Nhouse with a teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:05.20,Main,boy,0000,0000,0000,,Why's an adult doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:06.71,Main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:09.47,Main,att,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:14.35,Main,att,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to land, so please return \Nyour seat and tray to the upright position.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:15.75,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.33,Main,att,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.48,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,One Police Plaza building, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.74,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to New York, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:37.98,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And welcome to the Strategic \NResponse Group HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.92,sign_3955_24_NYPD_HQ__One_Pol,txt,0000,0000,0000,,NYPD HQ\N{\fs22}"One Police Plaza"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:39.23,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:42.92,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm Akari Kido from the Tokyo \NMetropolitan Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.74,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:51.26,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to have you here as the first \Ncooperation exchange intern from the TMPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:55.02,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from your record, nobody \Nwould be better suited than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:58.53,sign_3955_24_NYPD_HQ__One_Pol,txt,0000,0000,0000,,New York City Police Department \N{\fs22}Strategic Response Group
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.66,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm sorry, everyone's currently out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.37,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We'll have formal introductions tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:03.40,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should apologize for arriving \Nthe day before beginning my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.91,sign_4638_33_New_York_City_Po,txt,0000,0000,0000,,New York City Police Department Strategic Response Group\N{\fs22}Superintendent Victoria Johansson
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.94,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As the NYPD's most respected superior,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:08.41,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I know your father would be happy, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.90,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:12.17,sign_4638_33_New_York_City_Po,txt,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Metropolitan Police Department Mobile Investigation Unit\N{\fs22}Police Officer Akari Kido (Temporary)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:14.74,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My father would probably be \Nsurprised to see me here at his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.75,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:20.05,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,During your internship, you'll be working \Nas part of our investigation unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:23.17,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Try to take in as much as possible, \Nfor your future career, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:27.82,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I will. My father often used to say, \N"I'm going to protect New York."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:31.44,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping to get a little bit \Ncloser to that sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.32,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.60,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:39.16,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Akari, that's Emma, your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.24,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Akari Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.04,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.84,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I'm Emma Wattstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.21,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "huh" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:52.55,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought, "Is she Emma \NWatson or Emma Stone? Nope!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:56.40,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,"She looks nothing like those \Npretty film stars, anyway," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.99,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I didn't! I really didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:02.34,sign_4638_33_New_York_City_Po,txt,0000,0000,0000,,New York City Police Department Strategic Response Group \N{\fs22}Police Officer Emma Wattstone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.07,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A likely story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:02.33,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I promise, I really didn't think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.05,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you two have hit it off already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.31,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.43,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Akari, good luck starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.19,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:13.90,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, please take Akari to her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.90,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.50,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.91,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:17.46,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:29.81,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care, but your crafted \Npersona is super obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.46,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Or is that the Japanese style?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.99,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to work with a teddy bear in your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.44,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I just—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:43.28,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,I had to wait for freaking ever just for \Nsome newbie coming from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:46.27,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,It's this late already? \NNo wonder I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:49.60,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to deal with this \Non Christmas? My life sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.59,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.02,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. What'll it be today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.73,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,From here to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.69,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,How can you like donuts that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.50,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:21.33,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a Christmas party for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.40,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,My gut's finally stopped growling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.70,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how can you like \Nthat teddy bear so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.32,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you bring it to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:03.00,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something valuable in it, \Nlike jewels? Secret blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.84,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell me it was \Na present from your daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:12.92,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's it. It's a present he left \Nbehind for me the day he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:17.88,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,It's my most important friend. \NIt's basically my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.32,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad, he—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:28.71,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he died in the line of duty \Nfifteen years ago, on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:36.06,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,This teddy bear's name is Apple. \NI feel safe when we're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.28,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'm with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:46.34,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't help wondering what \Nmade my father choose this bear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.68,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,for my present that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:53.50,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,My only regret now is that I \Ndidn't get to thank him for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.51,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hit me right in the feels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.96,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I cry easily, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.70,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Eye in my sugar! Sugar in my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:09.48,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,God damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.45,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right, Emma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.47,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.70,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,You'd best not be late on \Nyour first day tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.77,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,You got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.13,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.91,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving me \Na lift tonight, Ms. Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.63,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Emma's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:32.37,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, buddies can't be all formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:34.67,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.60,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.15,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.33,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:09.29,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Until I got here, I thought that \NChristmas in New York would be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:13.76,Main,appl,0000,0000,0000,,Emma sounds gruff, but she \Nseems like a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What have we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.06,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.76,phone,,0000,0000,0000,,Alarm\N{\fs16\c&HB4A281&}Tap for snooze mode
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.36,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,What? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.13,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh? Eh? Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:35.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.88,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first intern in \Nthe cooperative program
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.84,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,between the NYPD and the \NTokyo Metropolitan Police,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:51.52,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,First Response Investigation \NOfficer Akari Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.74,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.24,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,What? Your bear was stolen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:03.56,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up this morning, it was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.70,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:09.79,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,I won't comment on that, but you're going \Nto freeze to death dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:17.21,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When you think of Christmas and the NYPD, \Nyou think of this: traffic control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:17.22,sign_14941_134_NYPD_s_Winter_Sp,txt,0000,0000,0000,,NYPD's Winter Spectacle: {\fs22}Traffic Control
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:25.09,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,And when you come to New York any \Ntime of the year, you gotta have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:29.65,sign_14941_134_NYPD_s_Winter_Sp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}New York Specialty: {\fs22}Hot Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.63,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's nothing better for \Nmy frozen body than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:34.60,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, New York's Christmas \Nis the best in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:39.12,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,That's why so many people flock \Nhere from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:46.61,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't a nice guy or two fall \Nfrom the sky for me? Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.75,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:00.67,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:14.48,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,I did hear that they were shooting a \Nmovie, but I didn't know it was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.53,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,A movie? That looks so real!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:24.63,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! It's time for our \Nsparkling Christmas to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.63,Main,cops,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.27,Main,cop2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.63,Main,cop2,0000,0000,0000,,Guns don't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.75,Main,cop,0000,0000,0000,,My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:47.20,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a movie shoot! \NIt's an actual emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.11,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Akari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:54.15,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all of you, time to start moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.02,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:02.04,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,Merry, merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.39,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,Have lots of fun, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:11.29,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, my greatest pleasure \Nis to see people having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:19.96,Main,mon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't interrupt my Christmas party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.61,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe now, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.61,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect New York and you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.90,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.08,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:07.18,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Big Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.24,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.83,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:28.42,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,We've always been together, ever since \NDad gave me to you as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.38,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.09,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.73,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,That's so weird! You're Apple, \Nbut you have no fur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:38.68,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:41.57,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,That's so weird! You're Apple, \Nbut you're not a stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.57,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.52,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,You're Apple, but you're super strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.65,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:47.54,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Liberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:50.99,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! I'm everyone's idol, Liberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:55.83,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, bear, why are you the only one \Nwho turned into some kind of hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.43,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:02.04,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to keep on \Npumping up this party. Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.63,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.16,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.27,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,A toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:18.61,Italics,wom,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fortunately, there were no \Ncasualties when the giant snowmen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.20,Italics,wom,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and toys appeared out of nowhere \Nhere in snowy New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.82,Italics,wom,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It is thought that this was some \Nsort of publicity stunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:27.37,Italics,wom,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but as of yet, nobody has \Nclaimed responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.91,Italics,wom,0000,0000,0000,,This is a video submitted \Nby one of our viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.12,Italics,guy,0000,0000,0000,,This was an attack by monsters! \NThis was a monster str—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.18,Italics,wom,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is all we have from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.64,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,You said your name was Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.77,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,So are you a bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.93,Main,appl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.25,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Are you human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.13,Main,appl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:53.09,Main,appl,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been with Akari, \Never since that Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.26,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,That Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:09.29,Italics,aka,0000,0000,0000,,It was when my family was \Nstill living in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:12.57,Flashback,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, when are you coming home today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:17.52,Flashback,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom said we're having a big \Nfeast with turkey and cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.40,Flashback,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.54,Flashback,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to come home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.14,Flashback,aka,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.76,Flashback,dad,0000,0000,0000,,But here's something you'll like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:30.00,Flashback,dad,0000,0000,0000,,This year you'll get a present not just \Nfrom Santa, but from me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.68,Flashback,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What? What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:34.58,Flashback,dad,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see when you wake up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.10,Flashback,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:39.01,Flashback,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Work hard, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.10,Flashback,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sure will. I'm going to protect New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:46.48,Flashback,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Especially because tonight is Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.80,Flashback,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:57.50,Italics,aka,0000,0000,0000,,But after he left for work\Nthat Christmas Eve night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:01.08,Italics,aka,0000,0000,0000,,my dad never came back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:12.15,Italics,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I named it Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:20.49,Italics,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Because the city that my father protected, \NNew York, was called the Big Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:28.08,Italics,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, we've always,\Nalways been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.55,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:44.08,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna lose all the salt in my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.88,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,So how come you're a human instead \Nof a stuffed animal now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:53.34,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I have this form \Nis because of that sorceress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.30,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorceress? You mean that \Nflashy girl from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.21,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.85,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Liberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:04.92,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,She can give life to all sorts \Nof things with her magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.40,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:10.43,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why all the toys started \Ntheir rampage in the city earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:11.16,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:16.96,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,That Liberty girl was saying that she \Nwas going to keep pumping up the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.34,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,What is she really trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.85,Italics,vic,0000,0000,0000,,As you've heard, the actions, \Nmotives, and abilities of Liberty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.24,Italics,vic,0000,0000,0000,,the suspected mastermind \Nbehind this case, are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.64,Italics,vic,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many question marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:58.12,Italics,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Our first priority is to determine \Nwhat she's after, so that we can keep
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.79,Italics,vic,0000,0000,0000,,the chaos to a minimum this Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.73,Italics,vic,0000,0000,0000,,That said, firearms don't work against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:06.19,Main,vic,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, please be extra vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.23,Italics,vic,0000,0000,0000,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:11.37,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to be vigilant \Nagainst someone who can use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:14.35,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Start wizard training right now or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.93,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.66,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:24.22,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Akari. \NI'm going to capture Liberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:25.84,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:47.41,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Let's play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.17,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this an unforgettable Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.13,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:58.03,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you want me to play with you, little bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.22,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,You're good, little bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.02,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.79,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:44.88,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll grant you this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:48.11,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Happy holidays!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.67,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:24.13,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:59.59,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, you can't sit in the\Ndark like this on Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:01.00,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Wakey, wakey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.41,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:10.99,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you just never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:28.49,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.42,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:55.57,Main,giuy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.19,Main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:22:58.83,Main,kid,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.36,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the times for this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:02.56,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:06.78,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,It's at the American Museum \Nof Natural History.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:08.96,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,That's where Apple went.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:13.95,Main,appl,0000,0000,0000,,What... is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:19.76,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,He's absorbing the city's electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.26,Main,mob,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:26.35,Main,mob,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:29.22,Main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,For your own safety, \Nplease do not leave your vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:31.12,Main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,HQ, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:33.60,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:34.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:35.85,Main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,Happy holidays!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:40.30,Italics,wom,0000,0000,0000,,Collision between motorbike and \Nbicycle on 42nd by the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:41.96,Italics,wom,0000,0000,0000,,Requesting an ambulance stat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:44.15,Italics,guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's the scale of this blackout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:46.50,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,We need to go after Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:48.86,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,But you see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:54.20,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:59.55,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, but I need to borrow this!\NI'll return it afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:00.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Bu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:01.81,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Please contact me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:06.57,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I can't read Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:07.35,sign_34847_287_Tokyo_Metropolit,txt,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Metropolitan Police Department \NMobile Investigation Unit\NPolice Officer Akari Kido
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:09.40,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right at the next intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:12.45,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,There should be fewer people \Nthere, so you can go faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.45,0:24:13.04,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.04,0:24:15.51,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the navigating to me. \NAnd the pedaling—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:17.10,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.60,0:24:32.72,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,This is like an entirely different city.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.94,0:24:34.78,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.78,0:24:38.51,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Any city will look nice from far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.51,0:24:41.42,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,but the closer you get, the more \Nyou see the grime and dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.42,0:24:43.81,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,That's especially true for New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:46.42,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.83,0:24:49.92,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,There are things you can't \Nfind out unless you get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.04,0:24:54.06,Main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.06,0:24:55.47,Main,old,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.63,0:24:57.56,Main,kids,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.57,0:25:01.84,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see that kind \Nof light from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.67,0:25:05.01,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.65,0:25:08.86,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have seen who you are \Nif I hadn't gotten closer, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.24,0:25:14.08,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,You're more abrasive and rough \Nthan anyone in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.49,0:25:18.17,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality, you're a wonderful \Nperson who cries easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:20.42,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have seen that from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.73,0:25:26.63,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't think you've gotten \Nclose to me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.83,0:25:30.10,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, we're going to protect this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.83,0:25:32.45,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Better believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.59,0:25:44.75,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:46.77,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple! Apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.53,0:25:53.90,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,What is that monster now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:58.24,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,He's the source of this darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.24,0:25:59.56,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.56,0:26:00.66,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.00,0:26:04.33,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.33,0:26:08.25,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! We'll be right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.66,0:26:09.55,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.99,0:26:15.96,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, you and \NI will always be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.24,0:26:18.24,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.43,0:26:26.90,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,That said, how are we going to chase them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.45,0:26:30.50,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.51,0:26:37.92,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this might come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.92,0:26:38.99,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.99,0:26:40.97,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to chasing, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.97,0:26:41.76,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.12,0:26:56.54,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.33,0:26:58.51,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Liberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.68,0:27:03.71,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, little bear. Stop struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.40,0:27:09.65,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it kinda look like we \Nawakened some serious trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.65,0:27:10.71,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.99,0:27:13.98,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what do you mean, "we"?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.99,0:27:20.89,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akari, even if we do catch up to that \Nthing, what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.89,0:27:23.96,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But we have \Nto stop him somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.21,0:27:32.52,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.52,0:27:33.73,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.73,0:27:37.00,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a happy, happy, \Nhappy Christmas for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.00,0:27:38.79,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't everyone's Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.79,0:27:40.68,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.59,0:27:44.31,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get serious now!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.33,0:27:50.28,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Give New York its light back!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.28,0:27:52.11,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.18,0:27:57.94,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Where are his arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.35,0:28:10.09,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.87,0:28:17.87,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.78,0:28:27.27,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.68,0:28:37.05,Main,book,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mister Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.05,0:28:38.69,Main,book,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.69,0:28:40.29,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.29,0:28:41.73,Main,book,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.62,0:28:49.03,Main,emp,0000,0000,0000,,My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.03,0:28:52.80,Main,emp,0000,0000,0000,,Gigantic Shuriken Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.03,0:29:08.22,Main,emp,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.48,0:29:12.51,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.76,0:29:29.30,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,That was too close! We almost died!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.32,0:29:32.42,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Akari, you're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.21,0:29:35.20,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.20,0:29:36.51,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.51,0:29:39.19,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,A woman's life depends on \Nher face. And her hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.19,0:29:41.62,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,A woman's life depends \Non all sorts of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.62,0:29:42.63,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.56,0:29:47.81,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,It's the helicopter pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.81,0:29:48.98,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.98,0:29:51.93,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's a cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.93,0:29:53.87,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave this one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.11,0:29:56.80,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.43,0:29:59.86,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.86,0:30:03.07,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! My favorite dress is in tatters!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.07,0:30:04.25,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Liberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.99,0:30:10.40,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're that bear's owner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.40,0:30:13.62,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Liberty, you're behind all this chaos, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.62,0:30:15.43,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I might be!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.21,0:30:16.96,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.96,0:30:17.63,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.63,0:30:20.00,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I said I was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.31,0:30:23.02,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for it, kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.41,0:30:33.98,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,So, officer, are you a good shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.46,0:30:36.80,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.19,0:30:43.32,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.86,0:30:45.78,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.28,0:30:59.93,Flashback,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I need a favor from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.45,0:31:05.09,Flashback,lib,0000,0000,0000,,During the fight earlier, there was a spot \Nhe was desperately guarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.09,0:31:07.76,Flashback,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, it's where he's vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.76,0:31:09.10,Flashback,lib,0000,0000,0000,,His weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.50,0:31:12.77,Flashback,lib,0000,0000,0000,,It's the eyeball inside his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.55,0:31:18.17,Flashback,lib,0000,0000,0000,,But his defense is essentially perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.85,0:31:24.61,Flashback,lib,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you to shoot \Nthat eyeball with your gun
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.61,0:31:29.24,Flashback,lib,0000,0000,0000,,while the bear and I face off with his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.08,0:31:37.05,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.92,0:31:44.64,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.83,0:31:51.21,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.45,0:32:08.20,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Liberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.96,0:32:19.91,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.17,0:32:32.13,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.58,0:32:35.02,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! It didn't reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.07,0:33:06.34,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.34,0:33:07.33,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.37,0:33:15.45,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Liberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.45,0:33:16.81,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.93,0:33:18.81,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.03,0:33:30.25,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.96,0:33:37.67,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple! Liberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.67,0:33:39.42,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.42,0:33:40.12,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.57,0:33:57.84,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.42,0:34:07.22,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect New York and Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.45,0:34:48.32,Main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,The lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.32,0:34:49.19,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.99,0:34:59.14,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,The electricity he absorbed is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.94,0:35:03.87,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,The city is shining again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.13,0:35:16.47,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honestly very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.47,0:35:17.77,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,This was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.77,0:35:21.92,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Look, if "sorry" was enough, \Nwe wouldn't need the NYPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.22,0:35:27.23,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Liberty, what did you mean when \Nyou said "everyone's Christmas"?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.82,0:35:31.69,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.78,0:35:35.16,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved this shining city.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.16,0:35:37.79,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved the shining smiles on people's faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.15,0:35:43.24,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,And above all else, I've loved \Nthis city's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.71,0:35:51.86,Main,gyu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.24,0:36:14.67,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,That man protected me when I was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.67,0:36:19.23,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,It was just for a brief moment, \Nbut he brought me happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.23,0:36:22.56,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, almost like he was Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.75,0:36:31.47,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,But I was so happy and \Nembarrassed that I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.01,0:36:34.60,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to find him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.40,0:36:41.89,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided that I'd make \Neveryone in this city happy in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.25,0:36:48.80,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,So that children like me wouldn't \Nhave to feel sad on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.63,0:36:55.27,Main,emm,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, your methods were too extreme!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.27,0:36:56.50,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Emma...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.10,0:37:02.57,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,And he was a really kind and cool Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.84,0:37:05.79,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,As I ran away, he called out to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.24,0:37:12.37,Main,lib,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't worry. It'll be all right. \NI'm going to protect this city."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.79,0:37:16.95,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,That was Akari's dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.25,0:37:27.21,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,I guess your dad protected \NLiberty's Christmas that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.47,0:37:28.24,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.29,0:37:32.82,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I understand what he meant now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.87,0:37:40.17,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,This is the city that he wanted to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.17,0:37:41.36,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.60,0:37:42.43,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.24,0:37:46.95,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can fall in love with \NNew York's Christmas again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.95,0:37:48.63,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I did when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.63,0:37:49.69,Main,app,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.13,0:37:52.25,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.65,0:37:54.90,Main,aka,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, Apple.
